explanation: The solution uses a list to store the text and an integer to keep track of the cursor position. The addText method appends the new text to the current cursor position. The deleteText method deletes k characters to the left of the cursor. The cursorLeft and cursorRight methods move the cursor left or right by k positions and return the last 10 characters to the left of the cursor.

